睇完wiki，話杜魯門唔幫國民黨，放任蘇聯幫嘅共產黨打下中國係左膠<br />\nFC：而家睇返on9還on9，但鬼叫蔣中正落曬奶力幫佢對家助選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 每逢有德國中東難/移民犯罪新聞，就會有人話德國左膠仲歡迎難民<br />\nFC：早幾年開始默克爾政府已經改變咗難民政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 馬克龍係左膠<br />\nFC：馬克龍banker出身，政策偏右，就連黃背心示威都係源於佢想加燃料稅，被低中階層國民覺得係搵窮人開刀而爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 德國圖林根州早前喺(唔知仲係咪連登最愛嘅)AfD玩膠、講明杯葛但又投咗票之下，選咗個本來只係Union+FDP推嚟做樣嘅FDP候選人做咗州長，結果佢喺抗議聲下被迫辭職，選返個左黨+綠黨推、本身競逐連任嘅左黨州長，跟住成堆留言話人左膠踐踏民意<br />\nFC：人哋州長根本唔係by popular vote，成件事來龍去脈都唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38063adefd11fa86e45f712bd0fe73b5457ddc2d","tid":2176541,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febb1878b799d1cc4f6e579adb4678b6ec5b4c61","tid":2176541,"uid":366165,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"我睇到標題淨係諗到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3nqLO8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3nqLO8.png&h=b15ba02e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61ed85c110a649f8d5fc008f1552fc7f88e61361","tid":2176541,"uid":16846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"febb1878b799d1cc4f6e579adb4678b6ec5b4c61","tid":2176541,"uid":366165,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"我睇到標題淨係諗到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3nqLO8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt